<a
class="tags--link link link-txt" href="/product/better-call-saul/" title="better call saul">better call saul</a></li></ul><h1 class="article-title" itemprop="headline"><em>Breaking Bad</em> Diehards: Your Clueless Friends Can Still Watch <em>Better Call Saul</em></h1><h2 class="article-sub-title" itemprop="alternativeHeadline">There's no need to miss out on the next show everyone's talking about.</h2>
</header><div
class="article-body article-articles
show-left-rail 		 show-inline-ads 				" itemprop="articleBody"><div
